        <zType>TEXT_EVENTSTORY_REPUBLIC_ELECTION_TITLE</zType>
        <English>Council of Oligarchs</English>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
        <zType>TEXT_EVENTSTORY_REPUBLIC_ELECTION_3</zType>
        <English>The oligarchs have gathered in solemn assembly. The great families of the realm must now choose who shall lead. Three candidates stand before the council, each representing a powerful house. The fate of the republic rests upon this vote.</English>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
        <zType>TEXT_EVENTSTORY_REPUBLIC_ELECTION_2</zType>
        <English>The council convenes with fewer candidates than usual. Only two family heads have come forward as viable choices for leadership. Nevertheless, the oligarchs must decide who shall guide the republic.</English>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
        <zType>TEXT_EVENTSTORY_REPUBLIC_ELECTION_1</zType>
        <English>The council convenes under unusual circumstances. With only one family established in the realm, the choice is simple: continue with the current leadership, or entrust power to the sole family head who stands as challenger.</English>
    </Entry>

